<item>
            <title>[LU-19667] kernel update [RHEL 10.0 6.12.0-55.47.1.el10_0]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19667</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) for kernel 6.12.0-55.47.1.el10_0:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: nfsd: handle get_client_locked() failure in nfsd4_setclientid_confirm() (CVE-2025-38724)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: e1000e: fix heap overflow in e1000_set_eeprom (CVE-2025-39898)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: wifi: mt76: fix linked list corruption (CVE-2025-39918)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: tcp: Clear tcp_sk(sk)-&amp;gt;fastopen_rsk in tcp_disconnect() (CVE-2025-39955)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: i40e: fix idx validation in config queues msg (CVE-2025-39971)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22571&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22571&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
